message.body: Hey! How you feeling about yoga tonight? Been so long!
I know! I have an online class tonight from 8-10 on functional blood work so I'm going to have to miss. I'm thinking Thursday will work though if you are interested!
Okay let's try for Thursday! I am being so bad at self motivating! Just wanna drink beers in the yard! Good luck with online class!
Haha yeah! The weather is so beautiful! Thanks for the luck, I'm excited to learn more about reading the blood.
